project_descr: Umbrella programme to cover anti-corruption and rule of law activities at central and local levels.

outputs.output_descr: This is an Initiation Plan for the COMPREHENSIVE PROGRAMME FOR PROMOTION OF RULE OF LAW, INTEGRITY,       TRANSPARENCY AND ACCOUNTABILITY AT CENTRAL AND LOCAL LEVELS” including anti-corruption work and support to rule of law EU accession agenda.

The project intervention is focused on the following components: 

1.	Raising awareness of the municipal management of the positive sides of pro-integrity reforms 
2.	Building capacity in the local administration to introduce an integrity system in the municipality  including through peer-to-peer exchanges of knowledge and know-how nationally and internationally 
3.	Providing assistance and support to the local administration officials to actually introduce the system.
